description:
Cort is a fun-loving and carefree kind of guy who really just goes wherever the wind takes him.

“I’ve traveled a lot and done a lot of odd jobs. I’ve been a firefighter, been in the military…I’ve seen it all and done it all early on in life.”

He also admits to being openly bisexual which peaked my curiosity right away. 

“Tell me more about this!”
“It just kind of happened one day after a long day on the job. A buddy of mine, we went out to get some drinks and next thing you know we were fooling around.  It was interesting to say the least!” He said with a huge smile on his face.
“Would you do it again?” I asked. 
He didn’t hesitate with his answer. “Yes!”
title: Cort
